11. Best Practices & Recommendations
Document every data mapping and transformation step.
Validate and QA at every lifecycle stage.
Maintain audit trails for all changes and reconciliations.
Use only non-PHI data in documentation, queries, and examples.
Stay current on regulatory and payer requirements.
